description:
This is a 9 minute workout called 'Guided 100 Squat Workout!' from the channel Jordan Yeoh Fitness.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along Jordan Yeoh in his 100 Squats Workout series, designed to enhance your lower body fitness whether you're at home, in the gym, or anywhere else. If you find the pace challenging, be sure to try the alternative exercises provided. Also, don't forget to explore my app for a variety of additional workouts and programs that will help you progress toward your ultimate fitness goal: https://bit.ly/trainwithjordanapp
